NOTES :

--------------------------------------------------
WHAT IS JENKINS?
--------------------------------------------------

    Jenkins is an open-source automation tool
    used for CI/CD (Continuous Integration & Deployment).

    It automates:
        • Build
        • Test
        • Deploy


--------------------------------------------------
JENKINS INSTALLATION (AMAZON LINUX / RHEL)
--------------------------------------------------

mount -o remount,size=4G /tmp
sudo yum update –y
sudo wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/jenkins.repo \
    https://pkg.jenkins.io/rpm-stable/jenkins.repo		
sudo rpm --import https://pkg.jenkins.io/rpm-stable/jenkins.io-2026.key
sudo yum upgrade -y
sudo yum install java-21-amazon-corretto -y
sudo yum install jenkins -y
sudo systemctl enable jenkins
sudo systemctl start jenkins
sudo systemctl status jenkins

explanation:

    Increase /tmp space (optional):

        mount -o remount,size=4G /tmp


    Update system:

        sudo yum update -y


    Add Jenkins repository:

        sudo wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/jenkins.repo \
            https://pkg.jenkins.io/rpm-stable/jenkins.repo


    Import Jenkins key:

        sudo rpm --import https://pkg.jenkins.io/rpm-stable/jenkins.io-2026.key


    Upgrade packages:

        sudo yum upgrade -y


    Install Java (required):

        sudo yum install java-21-amazon-corretto -y


    Install Jenkins:

        sudo yum install jenkins -y


    Enable Jenkins service:

        sudo systemctl enable jenkins


    Start Jenkins:

        sudo systemctl start jenkins


    Check status:

        sudo systemctl status jenkins


--------------------------------------------------
ACCESS JENKINS
--------------------------------------------------

    Open browser:

        http://<EC2-PUBLIC-IP>:8080

    Get initial admin password:

        sudo cat /var/lib/jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword


--------------------------------------------------
JENKINS ARCHITECTURE
--------------------------------------------------

    Master:
        Controls jobs and UI

    Agent:
        Executes jobs

    One master → Multiple agents


--------------------------------------------------
JENKINS JOB TYPES
--------------------------------------------------

    • Freestyle
    • Pipeline
    • Multibranch Pipeline


--------------------------------------------------
JENKINSFILE (PIPELINE AS CODE)
--------------------------------------------------

Example:

    pipeline {
        agent any

        stages {
            stage('Build') {
                steps {
                    echo "Building application"
                }
            }
        }
    }


--------------------------------------------------
REAL DEVOPS FLOW
--------------------------------------------------

    GitHub → Jenkins → Build → Test → Deploy


--------------------------------------------------
IMPORTANT FEATURES
--------------------------------------------------

    • Plugins
    • Pipeline as code
    • Integration with:
        - AGitHub
        - Docker
        - Kubernetes
        - AWS


