------------------------------------------------------------
EXITING & SAVING
------------------------------------------------------------

Press ESC first to go to Normal Mode, then use:
:
esc :w      → Save file
esc :q      → Quit/close
esc :wq     → Save and Quit
esc :wq!    → Force Save and Quit

============================================================
                DOWNLOAD FILES
============================================================

Using wget:
    wget <web-URL>

Example:
    wget https://example.com/file.tar.gz

============================================================
                EXTRACT FILES
============================================================

Extract .tar.gz file:
    tar -xvf file.tar.gz

Options:
    -x  → Extract
    -v  → Verbose (shows progress)
    -f  → File name

